reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great organizer AND cute
reviews.reviewText: What an upgrade! I used to use a single-compartment pencil pouch that I dumped all my writing utensils in, it was always just such a mess having to dig through it to find something. This helps with organization and it’s so stylish! This corduroy fabric feels high-quality. There are plenty of different compartments inside and outside of the bag. However, I wish the middle pocket served as a divider, but it’s designed with a gap underneath. Overall, still a great product!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect little pencil bag
reviews.reviewText: This bag is perfect for traveling with enough colored pencils to work on your current project. The pencil compartment will hold 20+ pencils securely since each loop will hold 2 pencils. I will use that compartment for the pencils I am currently using for a project. The other main compartment holds everything else you need such as erasers, blenders, paint pens, gel pens, extra pencils, a hand sharpener, etc.The quality of the bag is great and it is organized exactly as I needed. Love it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Big size and very cute
reviews.reviewText: Great size for the money spent, overall it’s very nice! I like the soft texture, and the amount of storage. I haven’t used it for school yet, but it seems like it will hold up all year. Small enough to easily slip in my backpack, but big enough to hold a lot.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for some who love having tones of stationary
reviews.reviewText: I've had these for about 2 month and they are great. They hold tons of stuff. I bought two in one of the I filled it with a bunch of my pens and pencils and in the section were there is individual elastic for each thing I put my big pack of highlighter.
